description:
Keep your travel essentials contained and together with peace-of-mind. Carry the RFID blocking pouch when you're exploring markets, or keep all your travel essentials together during flight connections. There's room for your passport, cards, cash, and even some cords and electronics.

  • Zippered main compartment has multiple pockets and a zippered mesh pocket
  • Removable magnetic pouch with RFID protection stores passport and a few cards
name: Thule Crossover 2 Travel Organizer - Unisex
